profile:
Southern Comfort Air Conditioning provides Quality Service to the HVAC/Refrigeration Industry throughout the Central Okanagan all the way down to the border. We are a licensed/bonded/insured company that focuses on both the commercial and residential marketplaces. Whether it is Strip mall HVAC systems, building Heat Pump loops, light commercial refrigeration, geothermal heating/cooling or your home comfort system we at SOCO AC have all your needs covered. 

We are licensed gas fitters and can look after your furnace or fireplace service or a new installation.
With over 25 years experience in the industry we have seen and worked on the majority of all systems and can help you with all your Heating and Cooling needs!
